title: About
text:
We are a group of four students of Sciences Po Paris, currently in our first year of Master of Research in Economics, and this Website aims to help us present in an extended way our work for our class of Microeconomics 2.
Feel free to reach out to us vie our academic email (first_name.family_name@sciencespo.fr) :

title: Microeconomics 2 project website
text:
Hello, we are a four students of the Master of Research in Economics of Sciences Po, and this is the website of our currently ongoing Microeconomics 2 project, focused on a game theoretical approach of pollution taxation.
